articles.title: Massive triumph in Johannesburg headlines South Africa's 2-0 series win over West Indies - ICC Cricket
articles.description: South Africa won the second Test against West Indies in Johannesburg by 284 runs, to finish their World Test Championship cycle with an emphatic 2-0 series win.
